---
import SEOLayout from '../layouts/SEOLayout.astro';

const title = "About OkayImBored | The Internet's Quiet Corner";
const description = "Learn about OkayImBored, a digital experiment in slow internet, built for those moments when you are endlessly scrolling but feeling nothing.";
---

<SEOLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>About OkayImBored</h1>
  
  <p>
    OkayImBored was built as an antidote to the modern web. 
  </p>
  <p>
    We noticed a strange phenomenon: it has never been easier to find entertainment, yet we have never felt so collectively bored. The internet used to be a place you <em>visited</em> to find something specific or explore something weird. Now, it is a place we <em>live</em>, governed by algorithms designed to keep us scrolling endlessly through a state of numb stimulation.
  </p>

  <h2>The Philosophy of Slow Internet</h2>
  <p>
    When you search for "what to do when bored" or look for a "bored button," you are usually handed another hyper-optimized feed of content. We wanted to build something different. 
  </p>
  <p>
    OkayImBored is a digital space that asks nothing of you. We don't want your data, we aren't trying to sell you a subscription, and we aren't trying to trap your attention for hours. 
  </p>
  <p>
    We believe that sometimes, the best cure for internet boredom is simply a quiet moment of reflection, a gentle interaction, or a reminder that there is a physical world waiting for you when you close the browser.
  </p>

  <h2>Who Is This For?</h2>
  <p>
    This site is for the 2am scroller. It is for the person who has 50 tabs open but nothing to look at. It is for anyone who remembers when the internet felt like a place of discovery rather than a slot machine.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you are bored, we invite you to spend one minute with us. It might not change your life, but it might just break the loop long enough for you to take a deep breath.
  </p>
</SEOLayout>
